===Proper noun===
'''Gemini'''

#{{constellation}}: A [[constellation]] of the [[zodiac]] supposedly shaped like a pair of [[twin]]s. It contains the stars [[Castor]] and [[Pollux]].
#{{astrology}}: The [[Zodiac]] sign for the [[twins]], covering May 21 - June 20.

